# INCarSignalOptionsResolutionResult

**Class**

A resolution result for the signals the intent is managing on the car.

## Declaration

```swift
class INCarSignalOptionsResolutionResult
```

## Overview

Return an `INCarSignalOptionsResolutionResult` object when resolving the [doc://com.apple.sirikit/documentation/Intents/INActivateCarSignalIntent/signals] property of a [doc://com.apple.sirikit/documentation/Intents/INActivateCarSignalIntent] object. Use the creation method that best reflects your ability to successfully resolve the parameter.

For additional resolution options, see [doc://com.apple.sirikit/documentation/Intents/INIntentResolutionResult].

## Creating a Resolution Result Object

- **success(with:)**: Creates a resolution object that indicates the successful resolution of the provided value.
- **confirmationRequired(with:)**: Creates a resolution object that requires confirmation of the provided value.
